profile:
Our Clients are #1 priority so we truly believe in high business ethics as far as relations with our clients are concerned. We strongly intend to develop a closer trust based on a long-term business relationship with our clients. Equally important to us is that our quality of products delivered matches the quality of our service. Our furniture is well maintained and spotless. If an item in our collection is damaged, ripped, broken or stained… it does NOT leave our showroom.
When you team up with Stagers Choice, you get more than a catalog of fine furniture, you get a team of professionals willing to go beyond to help you with your project and make your experience with us efficient & profitable.

We have flexible prices & lease terms and delivery all over GTA is available within 24 hours.

profile:
We specialize in furniture rental for home staging in the Greater Toronto Area, that will fit all budgets. Our furniture rental consultants have extensive home staging experience and can help guide you on your furniture rental selection. Whether you are showcasing a single room, a space-challenged condo, or a luxury multi-million dollar estate, you will find that our selection of high quality rental inventory of furniture and home accessories will meet all your home staging needs.

We carry an extensive selection of high quality furnishings to fit all budgets. Our competitively priced inventory spans contemporary, transitional, and modern styles and we continually monitor emerging styles in order to source new items.

Not sure of your needs? Our professionally trained staff can provide guidance to help you select from our broad range of styles and accent pieces in order to complement the features of any home.
